Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.43,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:00:59.60,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Put your hands up and slowly turn this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.37,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Damn! A contractor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:21.13,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, The suspect is moving northeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:22.30,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, He's a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.53,DTB-Default,Mayumi,0,0,0,, Report from headquarters:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.53,0:01:26.69,DTB-Default,Mayumi,0,0,0,, GR544 activity acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:29.23,DTB-Default,Mayumi,0,0,0,, His alias is Louis, a French agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:31.96,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Affirmative, direction of the wind confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.54,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Move the police to the east to circumvent him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:35.53,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:41.76,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Notice to all personnel: the suspect is a contractor by the name of Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:45.23,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, He has the ability to create a gravity block, therefore the use of automatic weapons is permitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.96,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Once confirmed, fire without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.98,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,, So that's the price of your contract, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.64,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,, Pretty troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.41,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,, Observer apparition... A Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:12.54,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.21,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,, I... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:27.05,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,, I'm telling the truth... a woman has the stash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:28.75,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.29,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,, Which syndicate are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:41.97,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,, Depending on the terms, I can retrieve the goods from the woman and have it delivered to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:46.06,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, A practical decision indeed, typical of a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.28,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Tell me more about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.65,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Yin, where are the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.67,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,, You have three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.51,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,, They're passing through Point A.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.21,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,, It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.35,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,, Let's pull out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.00,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,, Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.99,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,, If I don't come with you, the woman won't hand over the goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.27,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,, Hei, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.90,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,, We can still use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:21.25,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, People like you make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:21.86,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,, Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.58,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Boss, a star just passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.75,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.29,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Ten years have passed since its appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:40.07,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, It's getting difficult to remember how the scenery looked before the wall was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:43.12,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, What took place that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.53,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, and what lies beyond it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:46.88,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, No one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:53.70,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, The only thing mankind could do was build a tall wall and conceal everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.52,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, It was referred to as "Hell's Gate".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.96,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Beings with unique abilities, called "contractors",
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:05.42,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, and the existence of passive mediums called "Dolls"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.26,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, were said to have been identified one week after the appearance of the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.27,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\pos(640,568)}Tokyo Metropolitan Police\N Hatsudai Provisional Office
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:17.40,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Goes by the alias of Louis, his actual name is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:22.30,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, An agent contractor who's said to have connections with the French Foreign Security Secretariat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:25.66,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, His Messier code is GR554.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.37,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, He has the ability to create a gravity block.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:31.81,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,, At this moment in time, French authorities are denying any involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.20,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,, Cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:37.42,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, Unknown. There were no traces of asphyxiation or reactions to chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.46,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Do you think it's the act of a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.79,DTB-Default,Mayumi,0,0,0,, According to reports from the Division of Astronomy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:46.04,DTB-Default,Mayumi,0,0,0,, the stellar number of the prime suspect who was most active during that time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:49.88,DTB-Default,Mayumi,0,0,0,, BK201, an unidentified number.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.09,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,, Unidentified?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:55.64,DTB-Default,Mayumi,0,0,0,, Yes, every case he's been involved in has been left unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:06:00.35,DTB-Default,Mayumi,0,0,0,, The victim's cause of death and details of his abilities... We don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:05.11,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, Don't tell me it's that rumored "cursed" contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.99,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Rumors are merely rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.77,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Why are you guys, of all people, getting caught up in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.66,DTB-Default,All,0,0,0,, Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.24,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, What were the goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:20.13,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,{\fscx97}Confidential information obtained via illegal access to the central system of Pandora from the National Research Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:24.52,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,, As for the contents, we aren't authorized to know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.72,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, What about the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.32,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Shinoda Chiaki, twenty-six years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:32.21,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, She received her master's degree by writing a dissertation about the physical properties within the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.20,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, After graduating, she was employed by the National Research Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.60,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, She has been AWOL from work for the past two weeks. Her present status is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:43.71,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, There are reports of her involvement with contractor-associated cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.71,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Has her memory ever been erased by the M.E.?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.80,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Regarding her parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:51.80,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, At the time, it was concluded that she wasn't in contact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:56.71,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,, A leak of gate-related information is a direct threat to national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:01.08,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,, We must prevent the witness from falling into the hands of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.36,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,, Do you understand, Kirihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:04.72,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:11.07,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Ordinary people who come into contact with contractors have their memories erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:15.48,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, All information regarding contractors is to remain top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:19.03,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Even so, the rumors never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:22.21,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Monsters... Killing machines...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:26.86,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, Public sentiment towards them is that of fright and suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.23,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, My name is Kirihara Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:35.31,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, This case marks the first time the contractor, known as BK201,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:39.41,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,, and my Department of Intelligence's Fourth Division of External Affairs cross paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.32,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.55,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, What? Deliveries?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.60,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.85,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Cult solicitation? Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.53,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, No... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:22.60,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Oh, you're the gravestone salesman who keeps calling all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.19,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Stop bugging me! I told you I didn't need one yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.92,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, It's not that... The real estate agency in front of the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:31.21,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Oh, the electronics shop next to the realty agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.46,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, I've been waiting for you! Hurry in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.36,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, It's been acting like this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:40.17,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.09,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:41.82,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.60,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, The reception's horrible when you stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:53.39,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, You're the one who told me that if I switched to the digital whatever, there wouldn't be any static.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.99,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.41,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, This ain't a TV from the old days... You think you can fix it by doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.52,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.42,DTB-Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{\an8} They haven't disclosed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.30,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, It's fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.42,DTB-Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{\an8} And because it's enclosed under a thick veil...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.91,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.59,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, If I recall correctly, you're Li...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.16,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Li Shun Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.76,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Li-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.07,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, That's right. I heard from the realty agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.16,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Are you from China?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.31,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Yes, I'm an exchange student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:26.98,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Well, I know it must be difficult coping with the cultural differences and such, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.69,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Get along with your neighbors and don't cause any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.70,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.25,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Ah, Haraguchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:41.35,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, He'll be moving into this room from today...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.51,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, I'm Li Shun Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.08,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, Li-san, you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.14,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,, You don't need to force yourself to be too friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:54.88,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.55,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,, I've confirmed the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.47,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,, Show me what you're made of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.02,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,, The so-called black Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:53.65,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode One The Fallen Star of a Contract... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.61,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, Say, say, say, say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:03.44,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, I bet you're still in your teens, Ayame-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:06.18,DTB-Default,Ayame,0,0,0,, Come on, I'm already twenty-two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.76,DTB-Default,Ayame,0,0,0,, Oh, next week's my birthday, so come over and celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.20,DTB-Default,Ayame,0,0,0,, That goes for the customer over there as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.94,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:15.70,DTB-Default,Hostess,0,0,0,, What do you two do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.55,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:21.13,DTB-Default,Ayame,0,0,0,, Financial business? Loan sharks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.45,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.30,DTB-Default,Hostess,0,0,0,, Land sharks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.05,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, Why do you think that? It's a more respectable business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.63,DTB-Default,Ayame,0,0,0,, No way! I bet you're one of those folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.98,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, W-We're civil servants, you know, civil servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:36.72,DTB-Default,Ayame,0,0,0,, Come on! The only civil servants with such rugged faces are detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.28,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,, Excuse me, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.73,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,, It's time for the next rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:46.24,DTB-Default,Hostess,0,0,0,, Bye-bye. Make sure to call for me next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:49.04,DTB-Default,Ayame,0,0,0,, Next week... Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.19,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.90,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, I thought that girl looked like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.70,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, A completely different impression, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.59,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Women sure can masquerade themselves well with make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.74,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Isn't it risky to be in this kind of place anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:16.65,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,, Don't worry. We can write it off as a business expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:19.44,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, No, not about that! If the boss hears about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.36,DTB-Default,Hostesses,0,0,0,, Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.15,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.90,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,, Sir, it would be most problematic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.24,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,, if you were to act as a stalker toward our girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.54,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.11,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, This is the police! Clear the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.57,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,, Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.57,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Are you being chased?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:17.99,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.81,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.03,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, No, I have to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:26.84,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.89,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.82,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.27,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Were you gazing at the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:03.75,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.75,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, In the middle of the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.25,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:12.67,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Even when you know the stars in the sky are all fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.19,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.19,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Haraguchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.09,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.66,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, As I thought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.31,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, From Room 202?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:31.90,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, I'm Li. I moved in next door just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.90,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, I-I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.67,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:38.78,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.70,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Chiaki, it's me, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:27.74,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.96,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.45,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Jean, what's going on? Where's Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.65,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:36.20,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Louis was tied up with some complications.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:37.85,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.56,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, It looks like they're cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.27,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, They suddenly came into the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.25,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, They're already on to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.46,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Is there anyone else who came into contact with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.65,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, No... What happened to Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.47,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, I can't tell you much right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.58,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, All I can say is that he's taking refuge somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:56.99,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, You still have it with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.11,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:04.41,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Louis told me not to tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.54,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Not even a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.07,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Take me to Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.61,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, I know it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.72,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.51,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.40,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, No, get away from here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.12,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,, But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.04,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.20,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,,Lancernopt synchrotron radiation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.65,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Contractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:40.69,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,, Are you going to be okay with this kind of team?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.93,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Any changes to the plan can result in unexpected setbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.82,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, We have to act carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.72,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:54.59,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Doesn't it look beautiful when they're aligned like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.31,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, It's pretty difficult, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:18:02.06,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Then again, I have no idea why the hell I'm doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:06.73,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, This is the price I have to pay for my contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.04,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.04,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Louis is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:21.54,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, You're lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.42,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, It isn't a lie. Louis is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.56,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, He was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:28.90,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, It wasn't expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:32.81,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, for a contractor as formidable as Louis to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:34.83,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.98,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Louis was a contractor, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:41.56,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, That's right. You weren't supposed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.56,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Who was that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.08,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:49.01,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, The man who hit me on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:53.99,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, He's probably not alive anymore, but he seemed like someone you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.52,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.08,DTB-Default,Chiaki,0,0,0,, I met him for the first time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.21,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.19,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Not that it matters. We don't have any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:03.78,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, I'll use the quickest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:13.63,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, How insulting. I may not look it, but I'm pretty sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:19.59,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Even us contractors can be equipped with a personality, depending on the program,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.28,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, unlike Dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.23,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.42,DTB-Default,Man B,0,0,0,, I sensed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:30.75,DTB-Default,Man A,0,0,0,, It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.78,DTB-Default,Man A,0,0,0,,{\an8} There's nothing there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:34.47,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, An observer apparition?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.25,DTB-Default,Man A,0,0,0,, Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:38.21,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, Only contractors must be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.47,DTB-Default,Man A,0,0,0,, Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:57.58,DTB-Default,Man A,0,0,0,, That's strange. The security system for the electronic lock had a triple fail-safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.61,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.90,DTB-Default,Jean,0,0,0,, It's too much to be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:46.06,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The rain has stopped, but the starry skies that appear beyond the clouds are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:53.17,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Gentle words reach out to a closed heart, and the woman steps out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:57.25,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,, into the dark chasms of a bottomless marsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:04.59,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,, What the man sees in the fake sky is the shimmer of life that burns blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.92,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,, And a star falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.25,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(435,568)\c&HFDFDFD&}Episode Two The Fallen Star of a Contract... (Part Two)